list.item:
Guy Pauker’s Three Rand Papers on IndonesiaThese studies, done by Pauker for the Rand Corporation, were
                            RM–2619–RC, “Recent Communist Tactics in Indonesia,” August 15, 1960;
                            RM–2637–RC, “The Role of the Military in Indonesia,” September 1, 1960;
                            and D–8448, “Indonesia’s Drift Toward the Soviet Bloc,” February 3,
                            1961. The papers are 21, 65, and 42 pages long, respectively.
                            (Ibid.)
